and cannot be disclosed or sold to third parties. The readers of this site have the rights of access for reading only.
banglanews24.com
implements technology and security features in order to safeguard the privacy of its readers from loss, unauthorized access or improper use.
Users of the site are invited to inform
banglanews24.com
services on any dysfunctions of the site in the light of privacy rights.
If you require any more information or have any questions about our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us by email at
banglanews.digital@gmail.com
LOG FILES
Like many other Web sites,
banglanews24.com
makes use of log files. The information inside the log files includes internet protocol ( IP ) addresses, type of browser, Internet Service Provider ( ISP ), date/time stamp, referring/exit pages, and number of clicks to analyze trends, administer the site, track user’s movement around the site, and gather demographic information. IP addresses, and other such information are not linked to any information that is personally identifiable.
COOKIES AND WEB BEACONS
banglanews24.com
does use cookies to store information about visitors preferences, record user-specific information on which pages the user access or visit, customize Web page content based on visitors browser type or other information that the visitor sends via their browser.
